summary.en: Ever-trendy for its timelessly appealing design, this solid shift skirt from Forever 21 spells effortless fashion. Designed in a solid tone with a zip and belt detail, this skirt looks best when teamed with a high neck tee and boots.

By buying cotton products from Splash, you’re supporting more sustainable cotton farming through the Better Cotton Initiative (BCI). Better Cotton is sourced via mass balance.

summary.en: This checked skirt by Forever 21 is sure to make a bold style impact to your bottom wear collection. Moreover, you can match it with a loosely fitted crop top and a pair of ankle boots to make a standout statement for the day.
